additional_house_rules:
VISITORS AND OVERNIGHT GUESTS : 
No visitors or overnight guests without prior, express, written consent.
SMOKING, DRUGS, ILLEGAL ACTIVITY : 
No smoking, drugs, or illegal activity.
COMMUNICATION : 
All communication must be conducted on AirBnB through the AirBnB messaging portal.
PETS : 
No Pets.
EVENTS : 
No parties, events, or gatherings without prior, express, written consent.
THIRD PARTY RESERVATIONS : 
No third-party reservations. Person who booked the reservation must be staying in the unit; you cannot book a reservation on behalf of someone else.
HVAC : 
Turn off lights and all appliances (especially heaters and air conditioners) when you are not in the apartment, and do not run air conditioners with the windows open at the same time.
PAID/PROMOTIONAL CONTENT : 
Do not order any paid or promotional content or services under any account that is not yours.
LINENS AND TOWELS : 
Do not use the provided white sheets or towels to remove makeup. If sheets or towels are stained during your stay, you will be billed the replacement cost via the resolutions tool.
CHECK-IN : 
If you do not provide a check-in time within 72 hours of your date of arrival, please follow the alternate check-in instructions. These will be sent via AirBnB two days before your arrival. If you have confirmed your check-in time more than 72 hours before your check-in date, you may follow the regular check-in instructions.
CHECK-OUT : 
Check-out time is 12:00PM. Check-out instructions will be sent after your reservation is confirmed. If you know your exact departure time, please let us know.
MAIL : 
Do not, under any circumstances, have mail delivered to this property. Please contact us via the AirBnB message portal if you need to send a package, and we will do our best to help you find an alternate solution. If you have mail or a package delivered to this home without consent, we cannot assist you in receiving or recovering it.
NUMBER OF GUESTS : 
When making a reservation, you must include on your reservation request all guests who will be staying overnight at any point during the stay, regardless of age. This includes infants and children. Additional guests will not be permitted to enter, and if additional guests arrive after check-in, your reservation will be terminated.
FEATURES AND AMENITIES : 
You acknowledge that any feature or amenity not included in this listing is presumed to be unavailable at this home and will not be provided. Please ask any questions before booking.
SHOES OFF : 
Please remove your shoes and leave them by the front door.
QUIET HOURS : 
It is important to respect our neighbors. Kindly respect the building's quiet hours which operate between 10pm-8am. Excessive noise made during these hours is grounds for removal from the property, should complaints arise.

By requesting a reservation, you are agreeing to the house rules below.
https://www.airbnb.com/help/article/472/what-are-house-rules
 
1.     No smoking, drugs, or illegal activity.
2.     No pets.
3.     Please remove your shoes when entering the home.
4.     Please keep noise to a minimum between 10:00PM and 9:00AM, so as not to disturb neighbors.
5.     No visitors without permission, and no additional or overnight guests. All guests must be included on the reservation, including children and infants.
6.     No third-party reservations. The person who booked the reservation must be staying in the unit; you cannot book a reservation on behalf of someone else.
7.     All communication must be conducted on AirBnB through the messaging portal.
8.     Turn off lights and all appliances (especially air conditioners) when you are not in the apartment; and do not run air conditioners with the windows open at the same time.
9.     If there is an air conditioner in a window, DO NOT, under any circumstances, open that window
10.  Do not use the provided white sheets or towels to remove makeup. If sheets or towels are stained during your stay, you will be billed the replacement cost.
11.  If you do not provide a check-in time within 72 hours of your date of arrival, please follow the alternate check-in instructions. These will be sent via Airbnb prior to your arrival. If you have confirmed your check-in time, you may follow the regular check-in instructions.
12.  Check-out time is 12:00PM. Check-out instructions will be sent after your reservation is confirmed. If you know your exact departure time, please let us know.
description:
Amazing 2 Bed/ 2 Bath in Williamsburg, Brooklyn with a gorgeous and quaint private backyard garden! This is the perfect spot for you to explore Brooklyn or Manhattan, only 10mins from Union Square! I promise you will feel at home in my spacious and luxurious apartment. Live like a real New Yorker for a week at my spot, guaranteed that you will love the environment and neighborhood!!

1 bedroom + Queen murphy bed in main room.
2 Full Baths.
Private Backyard Garden.

I use a concierge service that can answer any questions or solve any problems that you may have during your stay!

Brunch and bike away the day and lounge and drink away the night in this infinitely hip warehouse-turned-loft Brooklyn neighborhood. New York City’s top spot for looking awesome while ordering beers that come in a tall can, Williamsburg is a food, drink, and music lover’s paradise. This ultra-trendy neighborhood completes its super cool repertoire with alternative-looking street art and two-story murals.

Only a few blocks from the Lorimer L Train Stop and the G Train. 
2 stations away from Manhattan. 10 mins from Union Square where you have access to the following subways: 456, NQRW, L

CitiBike anywhere in Brooklyn or you can even bike across the Williamsburg Bridge to get to Manhattan!
